headline: Teradyne Declares Quarterly Cash Dividend
summary: NORTH READING, Mass., May 08, 2025--Teradyne, Inc. (NASDAQ:TER) today announced a quarterly cash dividend of $0.12 per share, payable on June 13, 2025, to shareholders of record as of the close of business on May 22, 2025.

headline: 3 Profitable Stocks That Concern Us
summary: Not all profitable companies are built to last - some rely on outdated models or unsustainable advantages. Just because a business is in the green today doesn’t mean it will thrive tomorrow.
